        "text": [
          "ه عن أيّوب بن نوح فقد رويته عن أبي، و محمّد بن الحسن رضي اللّه عنهما- عن سعد بن عبد اللّه، و الحميريّ جميعا عن أيّوب بن نوح‌."
        ],
        "translations": {
          "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
            "Everything in this book that is narrated from Ayyub ibn Nuh has been transmitted by me from my father and from Muhammad ibn Al-Hasan - may Allah (swt) be pleased with them both - from Sa'd ibn Abdullah and Al-Himyari together, from Ayyub ibn Nuh."
